OL,3,CWoman arrested over autistic girl's
OL,4,Cdeath in golf course pond incident
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested over the
OL,7,Fdeath of an autistic girl who was
OL,8,Ffound in a pond on a golf course.
OL,10,FNyla May Bradshaw died at Doncaster
OL,11,FRoyal Infirmary on 30 March after she
OL,12,Fwas pulled from the water at Owston
OL,13,FGolf Course, north of Doncaster, South
OL,14,FYorkshire.
OL,16,FSouth Yorkshire Police said woman in
OL,17,Fher 30s had been arrested on suspicion
OL,18,Fof gross negligence manslaughter and
OL,19,Fchild neglect. She has been bailed
OL,20,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
