FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1776618353
OL,3,CWoman arrested over autistic girl's
OL,4,Cdeath in golf course pond incident
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Gary Magnay said: "Since
OL,7,Fthis tragedy, our officers have been
OL,8,Fworking hard to establish the full
OL,9,Fcircumstances surrounding Nyla's death.
OL,11,F"While initial enquiries indicated the
OL,12,Fcircumstances were not suspicious,
OL,13,Fthese ongoing enquiries have
OL,14,Fultimately led us to make this arrest
OL,15,Fand further our investigation in
OL,16,Frelation to the events leading up to
OL,17,Fthe incident.
OL,19,FAn inquest opened last week heard Nyla
OL,20,Fhad been taken to the Owston area by a
OL,21,Fchildminder.
OL,26,@nD@_OU
