PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1776618353
OL,3,CWoman arrested over autistic girl's
OL,4,Cdeath in golf course pond incident
OL,6,FCoroner's officer Jane McDonnell said:
OL,7,F"During the course of the excursion
OL,8,F(Nyla) passed through a gap in the
OL,9,Ffence and approached woodland close to
OL,10,FOwston Golf Course."
OL,12,FA search began after the childminder
OL,13,Fraised the alarm with police and
OL,14,FNyla's family, including police drones
OL,15,Fand police aircraft.
OL,17,FNyla was found unresponsive and face
OL,18,Fdown in a pond on the golf course. A
OL,19,Fcause of death has yet to be
OL,20,Festablished.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@ApmpD@FpnrD@TO]
