PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1776618353
OL,3,CWoman arrested over autistic girl's
OL,4,Cdeath in golf course pond incident
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Magnay said: "The
OL,7,Fheartbreaking loss of Nyla May has had
OL,8,Fa huge emotional impact - not just on
OL,9,Fher family, friends and loved ones,
OL,10,Fbut on the wider community.
OL,12,F"Nyla May's family continues to be in
OL,13,Fthe forefront of our thoughts as our
OL,14,Fwork progresses, and we will continue
OL,15,Fto support them throughout this awful
OL,16,Ftime."
OL,18,FThe detective urged people not to
OL,19,Fspeculate about the circumstances of
OL,20,Fthe incident.
OL,26,@nD@ZOU
