CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1776618353
OL,3,CWoman arrested over autistic girl's
OL,4,Cdeath in golf course pond incident
OL,6,F"Our entire community is heartbroken,
OL,7,Fand our thoughts are firmly with her
OL,8,Ffamily as they face this unimaginable
OL,9,Floss."
OL,11,FAn online tribute page was set up
OL,12,Fafter the tragedy which has raised
OL,13,Fmore than #20,000 to help Nyla's
OL,14,Ffamily with the funeral and other
OL,15,Fcosts.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@FO]
